#: ../../source/link.rst:4
msgid "Linking & Library Overrides"
msgstr "链接 & 库覆盖"

#: ../../source/link.rst:6
msgid ""
"In Blender, *Linking* is a powerful feature that allows you to reuse "
"assets across multiple projects without duplicating them. When you link "
"an object or collection from an external ``.blend`` file, it remains "
"read-only in the current project. To make changes, you need to create a "
"*Library Override*, which generates a local editable copy of the linked "
"data."
msgstr ""
"在 Blender 中，*链接（Linking）* 是一项强大的功能，它允许你在多个项目间重用资源而无需复制。当你从外部 ``.blend`` "
"文件链接 *对象（Object）* 或 *集合（Collection）* 时，它在当前项目中会保持只读状态。若需修改，则必须创建 *库覆盖（Library "
"Override）*，生成一个可在本地编辑的链接数据副本。"

#: ../../source/link.rst:10
msgid ""
"This workflow is especially useful for large projects and team "
"collaboration, as it allows multiple scenes to share the same assets "
"while ensuring that modifications are centralized in the source file."
msgstr "该工作流程在大型项目和团队协作中尤为实用，它允许多个场景共享相同资源，同时确保修改在源文件中统一进行。"

#: ../../source/link.rst:13
msgid ""
"However, when a character rig contains many rigid bodies and constraints,"
" managing linked armatures, library overrides, and related physics "
"settings can become complex."
msgstr "然而，当角色包含大量刚体和约束时，管理链接的骨架、库覆盖及相关物理设置可能会变得复杂。"

#: ../../source/link.rst:16
msgid ""
"To simplify this process, the add-on uses a :ref:`Root Empty <root-"
"operations>` as the single parent object for all auxiliary objects, "
"making *Linking* and *Library Overrides* easier to manage."
msgstr ""
"本插件使用 :ref:`Root Empty <root-operations>` 作为所有辅助对象的单一父对象，从而简化 *链接* 和 *库覆盖* 操作。"

#: ../../source/link.rst:20
msgid "Link"
msgstr "链接"

#: ../../source/link.rst:22
msgid ""
"When linking a character rig that uses this add-on, you typically only "
"need to link one collection — the collection that contains the :ref:`Root"
" Empty <root-operations>`."
msgstr "在 *链接* 使用本插件的角色骨架时，通常只需链接包含 :ref:`Root Empty <root-operations>` 的集合。"

#: ../../source/link.rst:25
msgid ""
"In practice, character rigs are typically linked from a *rig file* into "
"an *animation file*:"
msgstr "在实际工作流程中，角色通常从 *绑定文件* 链接到 *动画文件*："

#: ../../source/link.rst:27
msgid "Choose :menuselection:`File --> Link` to open the Blender file browser."
msgstr "选择 :menuselection:`文件 --> 链接`，打开 Blender 文件浏览器。"

#: ../../source/link.rst:28
msgid "Navigate to the ``.blend`` file that contains the rig."
msgstr "定位到包含角色骨架的 ``.blend`` 文件。"

#: ../../source/link.rst:29
msgid ""
"Open the file and select the collection that contains the :ref:`Root "
"Empty <root-operations>`."
msgstr "打开该文件，并选择包含 :ref:`Root Empty <root-operations>` 的集合。"

#: ../../source/link.rst:30
msgid "Confirm the selection to link the collection into the current scene."
msgstr "确认选择，将该集合链接到当前场景。"

#: ../../source/link.rst:38
msgid "Library Overrides"
msgstr "库覆盖"

#: ../../source/link.rst:40
msgid "After linking the collection, create a *Library Override* for it:"
msgstr "*链接* 集合后，需要为其创建 *库覆盖*："

#: ../../source/link.rst:42
msgid "Select the linked collection in the *Outliner*."
msgstr "在 *大纲视图（Outliner）* 中选择已链接的集合。"

#: ../../source/link.rst:43
msgid ""
"Use :menuselection:`Right-click --> Library Override --> Make --> "
"Selected & Content`."
msgstr "使用 :menuselection:`右键 --> 库覆盖 --> 创建 --> 选中及内容`。"

#: ../../source/link.rst:45
msgid ""
"Blender will generate local override data for all override-compatible "
"objects in the collection."
msgstr "Blender 会为该集合中所有支持覆盖的对象生成本地覆盖数据。"

#: ../../source/link.rst:54
msgid ""
"Due to limitations in Blender's current override system, it may sometimes"
" be necessary to perform the override operation **twice** to ensure that "
"all nested objects (such as rigid bodies, constraints, and helper "
"objects) are fully overridden."
msgstr "由于 Blender 当前库覆盖系统的限制，有时需要执行 **两次** 覆盖操作，才能确保所有嵌套对象（例如刚体、约束和辅助对象）都被正确覆盖。"

#: ../../source/link.rst:58
msgid ""
"This behavior is a known Blender limitation and is not specific to this "
"add-on."
msgstr "这是 Blender 已知的限制，并非本插件特有的问题。"

#: ../../source/link.rst:61
msgid ""
"After creating *Library Override*, you **Must** run "
":menuselection:`Update Rigid World`. See also :ref:`Update Rigid World "
"<update-rigid-world>`."
msgstr "创建 *库覆盖* 后，**必须** 运行 :menuselection:`Update Rigid World`。另请参见 :ref:`更新刚体世界 <update-rigid-world>`。"

#: ../../source/link.rst:63
msgid ""
"If this step is skipped, the physics simulation may fail to evaluate "
"correctly or appear to do nothing in the animation file."
msgstr "如果跳过此步骤，物理模拟可能无法正确计算，或者在动画文件中看起来没有任何效果。"

#: ../../source/link.rst:66
msgid "Overridable Properties"
msgstr "可覆盖属性"

#: ../../source/link.rst:68
msgid ""
"Due to the design of Blender's *Library Override* system, some properties"
" cannot be edited locally and must be changed in the source file."
msgstr ""
"由于 Blender 的 *库覆盖* 系统设计，某些属性无法在本地编辑，"
"必须在源文件中进行修改。"

#: ../../source/link.rst:70
msgid ""
"In addition, this add-on intentionally locks certain properties from "
"local editing to prevent accidental changes to critical physics settings "
"that could destabilize the simulation."
msgstr ""
"此外，本插件还会刻意锁定部分属性，禁止在本地编辑，以避免意外修改关键物理参数，"
"从而导致模拟不稳定。"

#: ../../source/link.rst:73
msgid ""
"Non-overridable properties appear **Grayed Out** in the :ref:`Properties "
"Panel <rigid_body_properties_panel>`."
msgstr ""
"不可覆盖的属性会在 :ref:`属性面板 <rigid_body_properties_panel>` 中显示为 **灰色**。"

#: ../../source/link.rst:75
msgid "Rigid Body Properties Panel"
msgstr "刚体属性面板"

#: ../../source/link.rst:81
msgid "If you need to modify these properties:"
msgstr "如果需要修改这些属性："

#: ../../source/link.rst:83
msgid "Open the source rig file."
msgstr "打开绑定源文件"

#: ../../source/link.rst:84
msgid "Make the changes there."
msgstr "在该文件中进行修改。"

#: ../../source/link.rst:85
msgid "Save the file."
msgstr "保存文件。"

#: ../../source/link.rst:86
msgid "Reload the overrides in the animation file."
msgstr "在动画文件中 *重新加载库覆盖（Reload）*。"

#: ../../source/link.rst:89
msgid ""
"When adjusting overridable properties during animation — such as *Rigid "
"Body Mass* or *Joint Angle Limits*, always save your file first."
msgstr ""
"在动画播放过程中调整可覆盖属性（例如 *Rigid Body Mass* 或 *Joint Angle Limits*）时，"
"请务必先保存文件。"

#: ../../source/link.rst:92
msgid ""
"Although these properties can technically be overridden, changing them "
"during active physics evaluation may cause **Blender To Crash** due to "
"instability in the physics solver."
msgstr ""
"尽管这些属性在技术上可以被覆盖，但在物理模拟正在计算时修改它们，可能会因为"
"物理求解器的不稳定而导致 **Blender 崩溃**。"

